recordsActions.text: Feci quod potui, faciant meliora potentes.
recordsActions.translation: Я сделал всё, что мог, кто может, пусть сделает лучше.

recordsActions.text: Feci quod potui, faciant meliora potentes.
recordsActions.translation: I did what I could, may those who are able do better.

recordsActions.text: Feci quod potui, faciant meliora potentes.
recordsActions.translation: Ich habe getan, was ich konnte, mögen diejenigen, die in der Lage sind, es besser machen.

recordsActions.text: Feci quod potui, faciant meliora potentes.
recordsActions.translation: Ho fatto quello che potevo, chi è capace faccia meglio.

recordsActions.text: Feci quod potui, faciant meliora potentes.
recordsActions.translation: J'ai fait ce que j'ai pu, qui peut, le laisser faire mieux.
